---
---

<section class="section-proof" id="prova" aria-labelledby="proof-h3">
  <div class="proof-inner">
    <div class="metrics-row">
      <div class="metric story-element" data-story-delay="0">
        <div class="metric-num blue" data-counter="68" data-suffix="%" aria-label="68%">0%</div>
        <div class="metric-label">de redução no tempo de relatórios</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric story-element" data-story-delay="1">
        <div class="metric-num ink" data-counter="847" data-suffix="" aria-label="847">0</div>
        <div class="metric-label">profissionais cadastrados em média por usuário</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric story-element" data-story-delay="2">
        <div class="metric-num green" data-counter="3.2" data-suffix="×" data-decimal="1" aria-label="3,2 vezes">0×</div>
        <div class="metric-label">mais follow-ups realizados no primeiro mês</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="proof-h3 story-element" data-story-delay="0" id="proof-h3">
      Propagandistas reais. Resultados reais.
    </h3>

    <div class="testimonials">
      <article class="t-card t-feature story-element" data-story-delay="1">
        <div class="t-feature-grid">
          <p class="t-feature-text">
            "A gravação por voz foi o que me fez assinar. Sento no carro, falo 2 minutos, e quando chego em casa o relatório já está pronto. Isso me devolveu uma hora por dia."
          </p>
          <div class="t-author">
            <div class="t-avatar">JF</div>
            <div class="t-name">Jamille Fritz</div>
            <div class="t-company">Natudermefarma</div>
            <div class="t-stars" aria-label="5 de 5 estrelas">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <span class="t-badge">Usuário desde jan/2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="t-card t-medium story-element" data-story-delay="0">
        <div class="t-stars" aria-label="5 de 5 estrelas">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="t-medium-text">
          "Em duas semanas o pipeline parou de viver na minha cabeça. Agora sei quem está esperando visita só de abrir o app pela manhã."
        </p>
        <div class="t-medium-author">
          <div class="t-avatar t-avatar-purple">MR</div>
          <div>
            <div class="t-mini-name">Mariana Rocha</div>
            <div class="t-mini-co">Eurofarma &middot; Linha cardio</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="t-card t-medium story-element" data-story-delay="1">
        <div class="t-stars" aria-label="5 de 5 estrelas">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="t-medium-text">
          "Era impossível lembrar quem havia pedido amostra na visita anterior. O MediVisitas resgata cada follow-up — e isso virou prescrição."
        </p>
        <div class="t-medium-author">
          <div class="t-avatar t-avatar-green">FP</div>
          <div>
            <div class="t-mini-name">Felipe Pacheco</div>
            <div class="t-mini-co">Aché Laboratórios</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="t-card t-metric story-element" data-story-delay="2">
        <div class="t-metric-block">
          <div class="t-metric-num" data-counter="340" data-suffix="" aria-label="340">0</div>
          <div class="t-metric-label">médicos organizados em 2 semanas</div>
          <div class="t-metric-sub">antes estavam em 5 planilhas diferentes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="t-metric-author">Roberto Alves &middot; Roche</div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-proof {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 120px clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-proof::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 80%;
    height: 60%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .proof-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .metrics-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .metric {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px clamp(16px, 3vw, 40px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .metric:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .metric-num {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .metric-num.blue { color: var(--color-blue); }
  .metric-num.ink { color: var(--color-ink); }
  .metric-num.green { color: var(--color-green); }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    max-width: 200px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .proof-h3 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 100px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .testimonials {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .t-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px;
    transition: transform 250ms, box-shadow 250ms;
  }

  .t-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }

  .t-feature { grid-column: span 12; padding: 48px; }

  .t-feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .t-feature-text {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 28px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .t-author {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .t-avatar {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-blue);
    color: var(--color-on-primary);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .t-avatar-purple { background: var(--color-purple); }
  .t-avatar-green { background: var(--color-green); }

  .t-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .t-company { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }
  .t-stars { font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-amber); margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 2px; }

  .t-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    background: var(--color-green-light);
    color: var(--color-green);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .t-medium { grid-column: span 6; }

  .t-medium-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 16px;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .t-medium-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .t-medium-author .t-avatar {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .t-mini-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); line-height: 1.3; }
  .t-mini-co { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }

  .t-metric {
    grid-column: span 12;
    background: var(--color-brand-bg);
    color: var(--color-brand-txt);
    border: none;
    padding: 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .t-metric-num {
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-brand-txt);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .t-metric-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .t-metric-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-brand-txt); }
  .t-metric-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-brand-txt); font-style: italic; }
  .t-metric-author { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-brand-txt); font-weight: 600; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .metrics-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .metric { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 24px 0; }
    .metric:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .t-feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .t-medium { grid-column: span 12; }
    .t-metric { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .t-feature { padding: 32px; }
  }

  /* === Animações de Entrada === */
  @keyframes slideUpFade {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes justFade {
    0% { opacity: 0; }
    100% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .story-element {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUpFade 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1) forwards;
  }

  .story-element[data-story-delay="0"] { animation-delay: 0s; }
  .story-element[data-story-delay="1"] { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .story-element[data-story-delay="2"] { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .story-element[data-story-delay="3"] { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .story-element {
      animation-name: justFade;
      transform: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>
